Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说所有萌文化都从秋叶原消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.57,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦…冈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎之穴和Animate都去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mandarake和Gamers呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么呢 冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋叶原不可能有那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才会绕路去中野买同人志嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理 你是在MayQueen打工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MayQueen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.13,0:00:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MayQueen喵喵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出要把萌文化引进秋叶原的…是菲利斯喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把否定这件事的D-MAIL发送到了过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅一封邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整条街居然被完全改变了
