Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 道什么歉啊 我说的可全都是真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.22,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部先生原来是这样看待我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不 琉华子 你是男…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.47,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没说够?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
